Connect with us

Imagine Your Impact

Choose opportunities and experiences that will bring even more meaning and momentum to your studies and your life. Join the club that will connect you to your people. Take a leadership seminar. Head to a service Saturday. You’ll feel a sense of belonging, explore your passions, and make a difference. Be involved in your community from your first day to graduation—and beyond!

Fall 2021 Student Leadership Consultants Team

What We Do

The Office of Student Engagement provides innovative and collaborative learning opportunities to empower all students at Ithaca.

Jumpstart Program
Find new adventures, resources, and friends as you transition to college life.
Clubs and Organizations
Follow a long-time passion. Discover a new side of yourself. Join one of 200 student organizations—or start your own club!
Leadership Development
Grow your potential. You’ll find 80-90 leadership workshops per semester—and your personal path to becoming a student leader.
Community Involvement
Experience the profound benefits of community engagement. Learn, connect, and feel part of something greater.

New Summer Hours

🌞SUMMER HOURS 🌞
